%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20The%20Richest%20European%20Royal.%20He's%20Not%20A%20Member%20Of%20British%20Monarchy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMonarchs%20no%20longer%20have%20ultimate%20power%20but%20many%20of%20them%20are%20still%20extremely%20wealthy.%20And%20some%20royal%20families%20are%20wealthier%20than%20we%20might%20imagine.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20reigning%20monarch%20of%20Luxembourg%2C%20Grand%20Duke%20Henri%2C%20has%20an%20incredible%20net%20worth%20of%20%244%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20royals%20of%20the%20seventh-smallest%20nation%20in%20Europe%20might%20not%20be%20as%20popular%20as%20their%20British%20counterparts%2C%20but%20they%20have%20accumulated%20a%20sizeable%20fortune.%20Even%20King%20Charles%20and%20Queen%20Camilla's%20estimated%20net%20worth%20stands%20nowhere%20compared%20to%20Duke%20Henri's%20%244%20billion%20net%20worth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20current%20monarch%20of%20Luxembourg%2C%C2%A0the%2069-year-old%20has%20managed%20a%20dynasty%20of%20enormous%20riches%20and%C2%A0accumulated%20an%20incredible%20fortune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%C2%A0of%20the%20wealth%20of%20the%20Luxembourg%20Royal%20Family%20does%20not%20come%20from%20the%20multimillion-pound%20Sovereign%20Grant%20annually.%20The%20family%20gets%20only%20about%20%2411%20million%20per%20year%2C%20compared%20to%20nearly%20%24111%20million%20the%20British%20Royal%20Family%20received%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20money%20is%20used%20to%20cover%20staff%20expenditures%20and%20any%20costs%20associated%20with%20their%20official%20responsibilities%2C%20such%20as%20travel.%20The%20Grand%20Duke%20has%20an%20excellent%20real%20estate%20portfolio%2C%20unique%20jewels%2C%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20and%20private%20holdings%20--%20all%20contributing%20to%20his%20%244%20billion%20net%20worth.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHe%20has%20an%20extraordinary%20collection%20of%20jewels%20and%20a%20sizable%20estate.%20Duke%20Henri%20%E2%80%94%20the%20first%20cousin%20of%20Prince%20Robert%20of%20Luxembourg%20%E2%80%94%20owns%20three%20official%20properties%3A%20Fischbach%20Castle%2C%20Berg%20Castle%2C%20and%20the%20Grand%20Ducal%20Palace.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Grand%20Ducal%20Palace%20is%20not%20the%20Duke's%20primary%20residence%2C%20it%20is%20his%20formal%20residence.%20Located%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Luxembourg%20City%2C%20the%20Ducal%20Palace%20is%20accessible%20to%20visitors%20during%20the%20summer.%20Berg%20Castle%20in%20Colmar-Berg%20is%20the%20primary%20residence%20of%20Duke%20Henri.%20The%20gardens%20of%20Berg%20Castle%20are%20available%20to%20visitors%20on%20June%2023%2C%20Luxembourg's%20National%20Day%2C%20every%20year.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFischbach%20Castle%20served%20as%20Duke%20Henri's%20primary%20residence%20during%20his%20tenure%20as%20the%20heir%20apparent%2C%20before%20he%20officially%20left%20in%202000.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnDuke%20Henri%20caused%20a%20nationwide%20uproar%20in%202006%20when%2C%20a%20year%20after%20his%20mother%2C%20Grand%20Duchess%20Jos%C3%A9phine-Charlotte's%20death%2C%C2%A0he%20put%20some%20of%20her%C2%A0diamonds%20up%20for%20auction.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSoon%20after%2C%20the%20monarch%20came%20under%20fire%20from%20the%20public%2C%20who%20claimed%20he%20was%20selling%20pieces%20of%20the%20country's%20%26quot%3Bnational%20heritage%26quot%3B%20for%20extra%C2%A0money.%20Duke%20Henri%20consequently%20withdrew%20his%20late%20mother's%20belongings%20from%20the%20auction.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSpeaking%20of%20the%20British%20Royal%20Family%2C%20while%20King%20Charles%20and%20Queen%20Camilla's%20net%20worth%20stands%20at%20%24780%20million%2C%20Prince%20William%20and%20Kate%20Middleton%20are%20thought%20to%20be%20worth%20approximately%20%241.3%20billion%20as%20a%20result%20of%20his%20rich%20inheritance%20from%20the%20estate%20of%20the%20Duchy%20of%20Cornwall.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742623320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg