rent%20members%20are%3A%20Brazil%2C%20Russia%2C%20India%2C%20China%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20Egypt%2C%20Ethiopia%2C%20Iran%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20UAE%20and%20Indonesia.%20The%20partner%20countries%20are%20Belarus%2C%20Bolivia%2C%20Cuba%2C%20Kazakhstan%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20Nigeria%2C%20Thailand%2C%20Uganda%2C%20and%20Uzbekistan%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIssues%20discussed%20by%20BRICS%20include%20strengthening%20multilateralism%2C%20reforms%20of%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%2C%20Bretton%20Woods%20institutions%2C%20WTO%2C%20counterterrorism%2C%20health%2C%20pandemic%20preparedness%2C%20finance%20and%20trade%2C%20climate%20change%2C%20improving%20the%20international%20monetary%20and%20financial%20system%2C%20biodiversity%20conservation%20and%20promotion%20and%20protection%20of%20human%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELand%20degradation%2C%20desertification%20and%20drought%2C%20global%20water%20scarcity%20challenge%2C%20the%20exercise%20of%20navigational%20rights%20and%20freedoms%20of%20vessels%2C%20non-proliferation%20and%20disarmament%2C%20outer%20space%20activities%20and%20prevention%20of%20an%20arms%20race%20in%20outer%20space%20were%20among%20other%20issues%20discussed%20by%20the%20grouping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaishankar%20was%20also%20asked%20about%20the%20opinions%20of%20the%20BRICS%20member%20countries%20after%20the%20threat%20by%20the%20US%2C%20along%20with%20the%20likely%20role%20of%20India%20in%20this%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnderstandably%2C%20as%20nations%20at%20different%20levels%20of%20development%20and%20income%2C%20and%20bearing%20in%20mind%20their%20individual%20national%20interests%2C%20BRICS%20members%20have%20a%20range%20of%20positions%20on%20contemporary%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20meetings%20and%20discussions%20are%20aimed%20at%20finding%20common%20ground%20and%20working%20together%20to%20shape%20the%20global%20order.%20Their%20common%20thread%20is%20the%20commitment%20to%20multi-polarity%2C