was%20also%20Shahrukh%2C%20for%20Rs%205%20lakh.%20The%20second%20man%20took%20her%20to%20Rajasthan's%20Kota%20where%20she%20lived%20for%2018%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Bai%20said%20she%20managed%20to%20escape%20from%20there%20and%20returned%20home.%20%26quot%3BI%20did%20not%20have%20a%20mobile%20phone%2C%20so%20I%20was%20unable%20to%20contact%20my%20family%20members%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReunited%20with%20her%20children%20after%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%2C%20the%20mother%20of%20two%20has%20given%20her%20Aadhaar%20and%20Voter%20IDs%20to%20confirm%20her%20identity%20to%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%202023%20Murder%20Case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Bai%20was%20reported%20missing%20from%20the%20Gandhi%20Sagar%20area%20in%20September%202023.%20A%20video%20of%20a%20truck%20accident%20emerged%20days%20later.%20The%20victim's%20body%20was%20found%20with%20a%20crushed%20head.%20A%20murder%20case%20was%20filed%20in%20Jhabua%20after%20her%20father%20identified%20it%20as%20that%20of%20his%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20we%20filed%20a%20missing%20person%20report%2C%20Thandla%20police%20informed%20us%20about%20the%20recovery%20of%20a%20woman's%20body%20with%20her%20head%20crushed.%20We%20went%20there%20and%20identified%20it%20as%20the%20body%20of%20our%20daughter%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20tattoo%20and%20a%20black%20string%20tied%20around%20her%20leg.%20We%20performed%20the%20last%20rites%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20men%20-%20Imran%2C%20Shahrukh%2C%20Sonu%2C%20Ejaz%20-%20were%20arrested%20for%20the%20'murder'.%20The%20suspects%2C%20who%20are%20in%20jail%20pending%20a%20trial%2C%20have%20now%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20local%20court%20citing%20the%20woman's%20reappearance.%20The%20court%20has%20sought%20information%20about%20the%20matter%2C%20said%20Jhabua%20Superintendent%20Police%20(SP)%20Padmavilochan%20Shukla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5