ent%20for%20Muskan%2C%20stating%20that%20her%20actions%20are%20%26quot%3Bvery%20wrong%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20Saurabh%20Rajput%20deserves%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuskan's%20father%2C%20Pramod%2C%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20cracking%20the%20case.%20While%20taking%20Muskan%20to%20the%20police%20station%2C%20Pramod%20stopped%20the%20scooter%20and%20urged%20her%20to%20tell%20the%20truth.%20Muskan%20then%20confessed%20to%20the%20crime%2C%20revealing%20that%20she%20and%20her%20friend%20had%20killed%20Saurabh%20Rajput%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20were%20going%20to%20the%20Police%20station%2C%20I%20stopped%20the%20scooter%20and%20spoke%20to%20her%20and%20told%20her%20to%20tell%20me%20the%20truth...then%20she%20confessed%20the%20truth%20that%20she%20and%20her%20friend%20together%20killed%20her%20husband%2C%20they%20put%20his%20body%20in%20a%20drum%20and%20placed%20cement%20on%20top%20of%20it.%20I%20took%20her%20to%20the%20Police%20station%20and%20asked%20her%20to%20tell%20the%20truth...that's%20how%20the%20case%20got%20solved.%20The%20verdict%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20should%20come%20fast%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20want%20anything%20less%20than%20capital%20punishment%20for%20her...what%20she%20did%20is%20very%20wrong...my%20son-in-law%20should%20get%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20accused%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%2C%20Muskan%2C%20has%20confessed%20to%20killing%20her%20husband%2C%20revealing%20a%20gruesome%20plot%20that%20involved%20hiding%20his%20body%20in%20a%20drum%20and%20covering%20it%20with%20cement.%20According%20to%20Muskan's%20confession%2C%20she%20and%20her%20friend%20killed%20Saurabh%20Rajput%2C%20placed%20his%20body%20in%20a%20drum%2C%20and%20covered%20it%20with%20cement.%20The%20police%20have%20since%20recovered%20the%20body%20and%20are%20investigating%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuskan's%20mother%2C%20Kavita%2C%20regretted%20that%20her%20daughter%20did%20not%20share%20her%20problems%2C%20emphasising%20the%20importance%20of%20communication%20between%20children%20and%20their%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20tell%20all%20the%20children%20out%20there%20that%20never%20hide%20anything%20from%20your%20parents.%20My%20child%20has%20committed%20a%20big%20mistake.%20I%20used%20to%20ask%20her%20continuously%20what%20the%20problem%20was%2C%20but%20she%20kept%20losing%20weight%3B%20she%20had%20lost%2010%20kg%20in%202%20years.%20She%20hid%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20from%20us%2C%20and%20that's%20why%20she%20is%20in%20jail%20today.%20We%20have%20no%20idea%20if%20she%20was%20brainwashed%20or%20did%20drugs...had%20she%20shared%20something%20with%20us%2C%20she%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20in%20this%20condition%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Meerut%20City%20SP%20Ayush%20Vikram%20Singh%20identified%20the%20accused%20as%20Muskan%20Rastogi%20and%20Sahil%20Shukla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20person%20named%20Saurabh%20Rajput%2C%20working%20in%20merchant%20Navy%2C%20came%20home%20on%20March%204%20and%20had%20been%20missing%20since%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20SP%20Ayush%20Vikram%20Singh%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20based%20on%20suspicion%2C%20his%20wife%2C%20Muskan%20Rastogi%20and%20her%20partner%2C%20Sahil%20Shukla%2C%20were%20called%20for%20questioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20questioning%2C%20Sahil%20Shukla%20confessed%20that%20on%20March%204%2C%20he%20and%20Muskan%20Rastogi%20stabbed%20Saurabh%20to%20death.%20They%20dismembered%20the%20body%2C%20put%20it%20in%20a%20drum%20and%20sealed%20it%20with%20cement.%20The%20police%20have%20recovered%20the%20body%20and%20sent%20it%20for%20post-mortem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20said%20that%20the%20accused%2C%20Sahil%20Shukla%20and%20Muskan%20Rastogi%2C%20have%20been%20arrested%2C%20and%20an%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742618280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fnogf23n8_muskan_625x300_20_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnever-hide-anything-from-parents-meerut-murder-accused-womans-mother-7981825%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Muskan%20confessed%20to%20killing%20her%20husband%2C%20revealing%20a%20gruesome%20plot%20that%20involved%20hiding%20his%20body%20in%20a%20drum%20and%20covering%20it%20with%20cement.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Judge%20In%20Cash%20Pile%20At%20Home%20Case%20Was%20Named%20in%20CBI's%202018%20FIR%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJustice%20Yashwant%20Varma%2C%20a%20sitting%20judge%20of%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%2C%20at%20whose%20Delhi%20residence%20a%20pile%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-high-court-justice-yashwant-verma-fire-in-bungalow-cash-found-supreme-court-collegium-transfers-to-allahabad-7973039%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunaccounted%20cash%20was%20allegedly%20discovered%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20March%2014%2C%20was%20named%20in%20a%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20FIR%20linked%20to%20a%20sugar%20mill%20bank%20fraud%20case%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20registered%20an%20FIR%20against%20Simbhaoli%20Sugar%20Mills%2C%20its%20directors%2C%20and%20others%2C%20including%20Yashwant%20Varma%2C%20who%20was%20then%20a%20non-executive%20director%20of%20the%20company.%20The%20case%20originated%20from%20a%20complaint%20by%20the%20Oriental%20Bank%20of%20Commerce%20(OBC)%2C%20accusing%20the%20sugar%20mill%20of%20defrauding%20the%20bank%20through%20a%20fraudulent%20loan%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20bank's%20complaint%2C%20between%20January%20and%20March%202012%2C%20the%20Hapur%20branch%20of%20OBC%20disbursed%20Rs%20148.59%20crore%20to%205%2C762%20farmers%20to%20help%20them%20purchase%20fertilisers%20and%20seeds.%20Under%20the%20agreement%2C%20the%20funds%20were%20to%20be%20transferred%20to%20an%20escrow%20account%20before%20being%20distributed%20to%20the%20farmers'%20personal%20accounts.%20Simbhaoli%20Sugar%20Mills%20guaranteed%20to%20repay%20the%20loan%20and%20cover%20any%20defaults%20or%20identity%20fraud%20by%20the%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Yashwant%20Varma%2C%20who%20was%20then%20a%20non-executive%20director%20of%20the%20company.%20named%20in%20the%20FIR.%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Yashwant%20Varma%2C%20who%20was%20then%20a%20non-executive%20director%20of%20the%20company.%20named%20in%20the%20FIR.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F53r4k2bg_yashwant-varma-fir-_625x300_22_March_25.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYashwant%20Varma%2C%20who%20was%20then%20a%20non-executive%20director%20of%20the%20company.%20named%20in%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20allegedly%20submitted%20falsified%20Know%20Your%20Customer%20(KYC)%20documents%20and%20embezzled%20the%20funds.%20By%20March%202015%2C%20OBC%20declared%20the%20loan%20a%20fraud%2C%20with%20a%20total%20amount%20of%20Rs%2097.85%20crore%20lost%20and%20an%20outstanding%20sum%20of%20Rs%20109.08%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftransfer-not-final-step-top-court-has-sources-after-cash-found-at-high-court-judges-house-7975145%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BTransfer%20Only%20First%20Step%2C%20Top%20Court%20Probing%26quot%3B%3A%20Sources%20On%20Cash%20At%20Judge%20Home%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20figure%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%20was%20Gurpal%20Singh%2C%20the%20deputy%20managing%20director%20of%20the%20company%20and%20son-in-law%20of%20then%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Amarinder%20Singh.%20The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20later%20launched%20a%20parallel%20investigation%20into%20money%20laundering%20based%20on%20the%20CBI%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigh%20Court's%20Intervention%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202023%2C%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20ordered%20a%20fresh%20CBI%20investigation%20into%20seven%20banks%20linked%20to%20the%20loan%20disbursement.%20The%20court%20stated%20that%20the%20fraud%20had%20%26quot%3Bshaken%20the%20conscience%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20found%20that%20several%20bank%20officials%20appeared%20to%20have%20colluded%20with%20Simbhaoli%20Sugar%20Mills%20in%20passing%20loans%20amounting%20to%20Rs%20900%20crore.%20OBC%20was%20the%20only%20bank%20that%20approached%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20seizure%20of%20some%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdemoralised-delhi-high-court-chief-justice-on-cash-recovery-from-judges-home-7975094%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BDemoralised%26quot%3B%3A%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20Chief%20Justice%20On%20Cash%20Recovery%20From%20Judge's%20Home%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20order%2C%20the%20court%20stated%3A%20%26quot%3BBank%20officials%20completely%20ignored%20RBI%20guidelines%20and%20circulars.%20We%20direct%20the%20CBI%20to%20investigate%20which%20officials%20approved%20these%20loans%2C%20which%20members%20of%20the%20board%20or%20credit%20committee%20facilitated%20the%20disbursements%2C%20and%20which%20officials%20allowed%20the%20embezzlement%20to%20continue%20unchecked.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECBI's%20New%20Investigation%20In%202024%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActing%20on%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court's%20orders%2C%20the%20CBI%20initiated%20a%20new%20probe%20in%20February%202024.%20The%20objective%20was%20to%20uncover%20why%20banks%20continued%20to%20extend%20loans%20to%20Simbhaoli%20Sugar%20Mills%20between%202009%20and%202017%20despite%20the%20company%20being%20a