rate%20military%20flights%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20US%20deported%2055%20Indian%20nationals%20through%20Panama%20in%20commercial%20flights%2C%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20External%20Affairs%20Kirti%20Vardhan%20Singh%20said%20in%20a%20written%20response%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20was%20asked%20whether%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20received%20the%20details%20of%20the%20persons%20to%20be%20deported%20from%20the%20US%20this%20year%2C%20and%20if%20US%20officials%20were%20requested%20to%20provide%20them%20adequate%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20was%20also%20asked%20whether%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20raised%20concerns%20with%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20top%20US%20officials%20over%20the%20%26quot%3Bill%20treatment%26quot%3B%20meted%20out%20to%20the%20deportees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20reply%2C%20Kirti%20Vardhan%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOf%20the%20388%20Indian%20nationals%20deported%20since%20January%2C%20333%20individuals%2C%20after%20verification%2C%20were%20deported%20directly%20from%20the%20US%20to%20India%20on%20three%20separate%20chartered%20flights%2C%20which%20landed%20on%205th%2C%2015th%20and%2016th%20February%202025%20respectively.%20Separately%2C%20the%20US%2C%20through%20Panama%2C%20deported%2055%20Indian%20nationals%20who%20arrived%20in%20India%20on%20commercial%20flights.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20US%20Immigration%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%20authorities%20have%20recently%20shared%20with%20us%20information%20pertaining%20to%20an%20additional%20295%20individuals%2C%20who%20are%20detained%20in%20their%20custody%20with%20final%20orders%20of%20removal%20from%20the%20US.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20along%20with%20other%20concerned%20agencies%2C%20is%20currently%20verifying%20the%20details%20of%20these%20individuals%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MEA%20was%20also%20asked%20if%20the%20government%20has%20any%20plan%20to%20%26quot%3Bsend%20our%20own%20aircraft%26quot%3B%20to%20bring%20back%20Indians%20designated%20as%20illegal%20immigrants%20by%20the%20US%20and%20are%20to%20be%20deported%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20need%20to%20promote%20safe%2C%20orderly%20and%20legal%20migration%20while%20cracking%20down%20on%20illegal%20immigration%20networks%20was%20discussed%20during%20the%20the%20prime%20minister%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20on%20February%2012-13%2C%20the%20MoS%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia's%20consistent%20stance%20against%20illegal%20immigration%2C%20while%20seeking%20humane%20treatment%20of%20deportees%2C%20was%20reiterated.%20Both%20sides%20acknowledged%20the%20need%20to%20cooperate%20closely%20to%20aggressively%20address%20illegal%20immigration%20and%20human%20trafficking%2C%20by%20taking%20strong%20action%20against%20bad%20actors%2C%20criminal%20facilitators%20and%20illegal%20immigration%20networks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20is%20deporting%20only%20those%20Indian%20nationals%20who%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bapprehended%20for%20violating%20the%20US%20immigration%20laws%26quot%3B%2C%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIllegal%20mobility%20and%20migration%20has%20many%20other%20associated%20activities%2C%20also%20of%20an%20illegal%20nature.%20Moreover%2C%20those%20of%20our%20nationals%20who%20have%20been%20enticed%20into%20illegal%20migration%20have%20themselves%20become%20prey%20to%20other%20crimes.%20Those%20who%20have%20recently%20returned%20have%20testified%20to%20their%20harrowing%20experiences%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20batch%20of%20104%20Indian%20immigrants%20were%20deported%20by%20the%20US%20in%20a%20C-17%20Globemaster%20aircraft%20of%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%20that%20landed%20at%20the%20Amritsar%20airport%20on%20February%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20first%20such%20batch%20of%20Indians%20deported%20by%20the%20Donald%20Trump%20administration%20as%20part%20of%20a%20crackdown%20against%20illegal%20immigrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20treatment%20meted%20out%20to%20these%20deportees%20had%20kicked%20up%20a%20nationwide%20outrage%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US%20Standard%20Operating%20Procedure%20to%20organise%20and%20execute%20deportations%20effective%20from%20November%202012%20calls%20for%20the%20use%20of%20restraints%20on%20deportees%2C%26quot%3B%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20has%20strongly%20registered%20its%20concerns%20with%20the%20US%20authorities%20on%20the%20treatment%20meted%20out%20to%20deportees%20on%20the%20flight%20that%20landed%20on%20February%205%2C%20particularly%20with%20respect%20to%20use%20of%20shackles%20especially%20on%20women%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20flurry%20of%20queries%20were%20put%20before%20the%20government%20on%20these%20recent%20deportations%20and%20the%20overall%20immigration%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%202009%20to%202024%2C%20a%20total%20of%2015%2C564%20Indian%20nationals%20have%20been%20deported%20by%20the%20US%20to%20India%2C%20the%20government%20said%20in%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20query%2C%20the%20government%20was%20asked%20the%20details%20of%20the%20reasons%20and%20basis%20for%20choosing%20Amritsar%20as%20the%20landing%20site%20for%20the%20deportation%20flights%2C%20despite%20deportees%20belonging%20to%20multiple%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUS%20aircraft%20ferrying%20deportees%20have%20landed%20in%20India%20after%20securing%20necessary%20permissions.%20The%20landing%20site%20for%20any%20repatriation%20flight%20carrying%20deportees%20is%20decided%20based%20on%20operational%20convenience%2C%20the%20specific%20route%20for%20entry%20into%20Indian%20air%20space%2C%20and%20particularly%2C%20proximity%20to%20final%20destinations%20of%20the%20arriving%20deportees%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MoS%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20response%2C%20he%20also%20shared%20state-wise%20and%20date-wise%20data%20for%20the%20333%20Indians%20deported%20directly%20from%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20104%20Indians%20deported%20on%20February%205%20included%2030%20from%20Punjab%2C%2033%20each%20from%20Haryana%20and%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20three%20from%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20117%20deported%20on%20February%2015%20included%2065%20from%20Punjab%2C%2033%20from%20Haryana%2C%20and%20eight%20from%20Gujarat%3B%20and%20the%20112%20deported%20on%20February%2016%20included%2031%20from%20Punjab%2C%2044%20from%20Haryana%20and%2033%20from%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20also%20shared%20state-wise%20and%20date-wise%20data%20for%20the%2055%20Indians%20who%20arrived%20in%20New%20Delhi%20from%20the%20US%20via%20Panama%20on%20commercial%20flights%20between%20February%2020%20and%20March%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20date-wise%20figures%20stood%20as%20--%20two%20on%20February%2020%2C%2012%20on%20February%2023%2C%2011%20on%20February%2027%2C%20nine%20on%20February%2028%20and%2021%20on%20March%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742616060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fca7da76_ahmedabad-deportees_625x300_06_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F388-indians-deported-from-us-since-january-centre-informs-parliament-7981593%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20total%20of%20388%20Indian%20nationals%20have%20been%20deported%20from%20the%20US%20since%20January%202025%2C%20the%20government%20informed%20Parliament.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20to%20end%20legal%20status%20for%20532%2C000%20immigrants%20from%20Cuba%2C%20Haiti%2C%20Nicaragua%20and%20Venezuela%22%2C%22co