0Shoot%20Terrorists%20Right%20Between%20The%20Eyes%26quot%3B%3A%20Amit%20Shah%20In%20Rajya%20Sabha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20Friday%20in%20a%20sharp%20jibe%20at%20Congress%20leader%20and%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20while%20speaking%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20counter-terrorism%20operations%20and%20development%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20someone%20is%20sitting%20with%20%3Cem%3Ekaala%20chashma%3C%2Fem%3E%20(black%20glasses)%20on%2C%20how%20is%20it%20possible%20to%20show%20them%20the%20development%2C%3F%26quot%3B%20Shah%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20responding%20to%20Gandhi's%20remarks%20during%20his%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20in%20Kashmir%20in%202023%2C%20Shah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bone%20leader%20went%20on%20a%20foot%20march%2C%20went%20to%20Kashmir%2C%20played%20Holi%20with%20snow%20with%20his%20karyakartas%20and%20then%20claimed%20he%20saw%20terrorists%20from%20afar.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EArre%20bhai%2C%20nazar%20mein%20hi%20aatankwadi%20hai%20toh%20sapne%20mein%20bhi%20aayega%20aur%20Kashmir%20mein%20bhi%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20(If%20someone%20has%20terrorist%20in%20their%20mind%2C%20he%20will%20appear%20in%20your%20dreams%20as%20well%20as%20in%20Kashmir)%2C%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20the%20Modi%20government's%20zero-tolerance%20policy%20over%20terrorism%2C%20Shah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhenever%20we%20see%20a%20terrorist%2C%20we%20shoot%20right%20between%20the%20eyes.%20Our%20government%20can%20neither%20tolerate%20terrorism%20nor%20terrorists.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20speech%2C%20Shah%20highlighted%20the%20significant%20reduction%20in%20terrorism-related%20deaths%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20under%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarlier%2C%20terrorists%20from%20the%20neighbouring%20country%20used%20to%20enter%20Kashmir%20almost%20every%20day%20and%20carry%20out%20bomb%20blasts.%20There%20was%20not%20a%20single%20festival%20that%20passed%20without%20any%20worries.%20Even%20after%20this%2C%20the%20central%20government's%20attitude%20was%20flexible.%20There%20was%20fear%20of%20speaking%2C%20so%20they%20remained%20silent%2C%20and%20there%20was%20fear%20of%20the%20vote%20bank%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20arrival%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20the%20policy%20of%20'zero%20tolerance'%20was%20adopted%20against%20terrorism.%20After%20our%20arrival%2C%20when%20attacks%20took%20place%20in%20Uri%20and%20Pulwama%2C%20we%20gave%20a%20befitting%20reply%20by%20entering%20Pakistan%20within%2010%20days%20and%20carrying%20out%20surgical%20and%20air%20strikes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20outlined%20the%20steps%20taken%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20to%20strengthen%20internal%20security%20and%20said%20Naxalism%20will%20be%20eliminated%20from%20the%20country%20by%20March%2021%2C%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20working%20of%20his%20ministry%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20talked%20of%20the%20steps%20taken%20by%20the%20government%20to%20tackle%20terrorism%20in%20J-K%2C%20Naxal%20challenge%2C%20drug%20abuse%20and%20problems%20in%20the%20Northeast.%20He%20said%20the%20country%20would%20get%20free%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BNaxal%20problem%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20term%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20say%20it%20in%20this%20House%20with%20responsibility%20that%20Naxalism%20in%20this%20country%20will%20be%20eliminated%20by%20March%2021%2C%202026%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20Shah%20talked%20of%20the%20steps%20taken%20by%20the%20government%20to%20provide%20accurate%20intelligence%20to%20security%20forces%20dealing%20with%20Naxalites%20and%20said%20he%20has%20pity%20on%20those%20who%20think%20Naxalism%20is%20only%