e%20title%20two%20decades%20later%2C%20died%20Friday%20aged%2076%2C%20his%20family%20announced%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BWith%20profound%20sorrow%2C%20we%20announce%20the%20passing%20of%20our%20beloved%20George%20Edward%20Foreman%20Sr%2C%20who%20peacefully%20departed%20on%20March%2021%2C%202025%2C%20surrounded%20by%20loved%20ones%2C%26quot%3B%20Foreman's%20family%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20the%20boxer's%20official%20Instagram%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20grateful%20for%20the%20outpouring%20of%20love%20and%20prayers%2C%20and%20kindly%20ask%20for%20privacy%20as%20we%20honor%20the%20extraordinary%20life%20of%20a%20man%20we%20were%20blessed%20to%20call%20our%20own.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Texas%20on%20January%2010%2C%201949%2C%20Foreman%20grew%20up%20in%20Houston.%20The%20man%20who%20raised%20him%20was%20frequently%20absent%20and%20often%20drunk.%20Foreman%20only%20found%20out%20that%20J.%20D.%20Foreman%20was%20not%20his%20biological%20father%20after%20he%20won%20the%20world%20heavyweight%20when%20his%20real%20father%2C%20a%20decorated%20Second%20World%20War%20veteran%2C%20got%20in%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20adolescent%20Foreman%20flirted%20with%20crime%20and%20dropped%20out%20of%20school%20at%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%2013-years-old%2C%20George%20was%20about%206-foot-2%2C%20200%20pounds%20and%20the%20terrorist%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20younger%20brother%20Roy%20told%20the%20BBC%20in%202024.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20when%20you're%20bigger%20and%20stronger%20and%20think%20you're%20better%20than%20everyone%20else%2C%20you%20take%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2016%2C%20he%20took%20up%20boxing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20a%20football%20player%2C%26quot%3B%20Foreman%20said%20on%20his%20website.%20%26quot%3BI%20tried%20boxing%20just%20to%20show%20my%20friends%20that%20I%20wasn't%20afraid.%20Well%2C%2025%20fights%20and%20one%20year%20later%2C%20I%20was%20an%20Olympic%20gold%20medallist.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Mexico%20Games%20in%201968%2C%20the%2019-year-old%20Foreman%20bludgeoned%20his%20way%20to%20the%20super-heavyweight%20gold.%20As%20he%20celebrated%20his%20final%20victory%2C%2010%20days%20after%20fellow%20African%20Americans%20Tommie%20Smith%20and%20John%20Carlos%20had%20made%20a%20black%20power%20salute%20following%20the%20200m%20track%20final%2C%20Foreman%20waved%20an%20American%20flag%20in%20the%20ring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%206-foot-4%20(1.93m)%2C%20'Big%20George'%20was%20larger%20and%20stronger%20than%20the%20other%20leading%20heavyweights%20of%20the%20time.%20He%20was%20light%20on%20his%20feet%2C%20but%20slugged%20his%20way%20through%20the%20professional%20ranks%2C%20to%20earn%20a%20heavyweight%20title%20shot%20against%20champion%20Joe%20Frazier%2C%20demolishing%20the%20champion%20in%20two%20rounds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20he%20fought%20his%20third%20title%20defence%20over%2015%20rounds%20against%20Ali%20in%20October%201974%20in%20Kinshasa%2C%20Foreman%20was%20unbeaten%20in%2040%20professional%20bouts.%20He%20had%20won%20all%20but%20three%20inside%20the%20distance%20and%20had%20not%20needed%20to%20develop%20stamina.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAli's%20'rope-a-dope'%20tactics%2C%20exhausted%20the%20big%20man%20who%20lost%20in%20eight%20rounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defeat%20punctured%20Foreman's%20intimidating%20aura%2C%20not%20least%2C%20in%20his%20own%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20couldn't%20believe%20I'd%20lost%20the%20world%20title%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20later.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20most%20embarrassing%20moment%20of%20my%20life.%20It%20went%20from%20pride%20to%20pity.%20That's%20devastating.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20campaign%20for%20another%20title%20shot%20ended%20when%20he%20lost%20on%20points%20to%20another%20contender%2C%20Jimmy%20Young%20in%20March%201977%20on%20a%20hot%20night%20in%20Puerto%20Rico.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeman%20fell%20ill%20after%20the%20fight%20and%20said%20he%20sensed%20God%20telling%20him%20to%20change%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20retired%2C%20aged%2028%20and%20became%20an%20ordained%20minister.%20When%20he%20announced%20his%20comeback%2010%20years%20later%2C%20bald%20where%20he%20had%20once%20sported%20an%20afro%20and%20flabby%20instead%20of%20chiseled%2C%20it%20seemed%20like%20a%20boxing%20gimmick.%20He%20wrote%20later%20that%20he%20needed%20money%20for%20his%20youth%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnockout%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20three%20years%20he%20fought%2021%20times%2C%20mostly%20against%20mediocre%20opponents%2C%20winning%20every%20bout%2C%2020%20of%20them%20inside%20the%20distance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20big%20name%20in%20a%20weakened%20and%20fragmented%20division%2C%20he%20earned%20a%20title%20shot%20against%20Evander%20Holyfield%20in%201991%20and%20then%20against%20Tommy%20Morrison%20two%20years%20later%2C%20losing%20both%20on%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%201994%20he%20faced%20Michael%20Moorer%2C%20who%20had%20dethroned%20Holyfield.%20In%20the%20same%20shorts%20he%20had%20worn%2020%20years%20and%20six%20days%20earlier%20against%20Ali%2C%20Foreman%20was%20trailing%20badly%20when%20he%20caught%20Moorer%20on%20the%20chin%20in%20the%2010th%20for%20a%20knockout.%20At%2045%20years%20and%20299%20days%20old%20he%20was%20the%20oldest%20heavyweight%20world%20champion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20stripped%20of%20first%20his%20WBA%20title%20and%20then%20his%20IBF%20title%20for%20refusing%20to%20fight%20nominated%20opponents%20but%20won%20three%20more%20fights%20and%20was%20still%20'lineal'%20world%20champion%20when%20he%20lost%20on%20points%20to%20Shannon%20Briggs%20in%201997%2C%20aged%2048%2C%20and%20retired%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20fought%2081%20times%20as%20a%20professional%2C%20winning%2076%2C%2068%20of%20those%20by%20a%20knockout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201994%2C%20he%20put%20his%20name%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BGeorge%20Foreman%20Lean%20Mean%20Fat-Reducing%20Grilling%20Machine%26quot%3B%2C%20appearing%20smiling%20and%20friendly%20in%20the%20TV%20ads%2C%20becoming%20a%20celebrity%20outside%20boxing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeman%2C%20who%20hosted%20a%201996%20TV%20programme%20'Bad%20Dads'%2C%20married%20four%20times%2C%20fathering%2010%20children%20and%20adopting%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20named%20all%20his%20five%20sons%20George%20Edward%2C%20explaining%20that%20he%20wanted%20them%20to%20know%2C%20%26quot%3B'If%20one%20of%20us%20goes%20up%2C%20then%20we%20all%20go%20up%20together%2C%20and%20if%20one%20goes%20down%2C%20we%20all%20go%20down%20together!'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742611860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Flvl6iscg_george-foreman-afp_625x300_22_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fboxing%2Fheavyweight-boxing-great-george-foreman-dead-at-76-confirms-family-7981325%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20heavyweight%20champion%20George%20Foreman%20died%20Friday%20aged%2076%2C%20his%20family%20announced%20in%20a%20statement.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ranveer's%20dance%20performance%20at%20wedding%20goes%20VIRAL%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742611470000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119326148%2Cimgsize-56372.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Franveer-singh-shows-off-his-dhurandhar-look-and-channels-rocky-randhawa-with-his-electrifying-dance-performance-at-wedding-watch%2Farticleshow%2F119325542.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20al