port.%20However%2C%20state-run%20transport%20corporations%20such%20as%20Karnataka%20State%20Road%20Transport%20Corporation%20(KSRTC)%20and%20Bengaluru%20Metropolitan%20Transport%20Corporation%20(BMTC)%2C%20will%20remain%20operational.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20hotel%20associations%2C%20malls%2C%20bars%2C%20and%20restaurants%20have%20only%20offered%20%26quot%3Bmoral%20support%26quot%3B%2C%20essential%20services-including%20pharmacies%2C%20hospitals%2C%20ambulances%2C%20petrol%20pumps%2C%20and%20metro%20services%20remain%20operational.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%2012-hour%20shutdown%2C%20schools%20and%20colleges%20across%20the%20state%20will%20remain%20operational.%20However%2C%20with%20some%20transport%20services%20likely%20to%20be%20disrupted%2C%20the%20bandh%20is%20likely%20to%20impact%20Class%2010%20students%20who%20are%20appearing%20for%20the%20exams%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Karnataka%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20DK%20Shivakumar%20said%20the%20state%20government%20would%20not%20encourage%20a%20shutdown%20in%20the%20state.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20protect%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20state.%20Everyone%20should%20maintain%20peace%20and%20follow%20the%20law.%20However%2C%20I%20feel%20there%20is%20no%20need%20for%20a%20bandh%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20pro-Kannada%20groups%20such%20as%20the%20Karnataka%20Rakshana%20Vedike%20factions%20led%20by%20T%20A%20Narayana%20Gowda%20and%20Praveen%20Shetty-have%20refrained%20from%20participating%20in%20the%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBelagavi%20attack%20and%20the%20Maharashtra-Karnataka%20dispute%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20a%20conductor%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffresh-protests-in-karnataka-over-attack-on-bus-conductor-in-belagavi-rakshana-vedike-7791038%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKarnataka%20State%20Road%20Transport%20Corporation%3C%2Fa%3E%20(KSRTC)%20bus%20was%20reportedly%20attacked%20by%20a%20group%20of%20men%20for%20not%20responding%20to%20a%20passenger%20in%20Marathi.%20According%20to%20the%20conductor's%20police%20complaint%2C%20a%20girl%20had%20asked%20for%20a%20ticket%20in%20Marathi.%20When%20he%20said%20that%20he%20did%20not%20understand%20Marathi%20and%20requested%20her%20to%20speak%20in%20Kannada%2C%20she%20and%20her%20male%20companion%20allegedly%20assaulted%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20quickly%20escalated%20when%20a%20larger%20group%20intercepted%20the%20bus%20and%20physically%20assaulted%20the%20conductor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20police%20arrested%20four%20people%20involved%20in%20the%20attack%2C%20the%20bus%20conductor%20was%20also%20booked%20under%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20(POCSO)%20Act%20after%20the%20girl%20filed%20a%20complaint%20alleging%20'indecent%20behaviour'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20a%20bus%20driver%20from%20the%20Maharashtra%20State%20Road%20Transport%20Corporation%20(MSRTC)%20was%20attacked%20in%20Hiriyur%20Taluk%20of%20Karnataka's%20Chitradurga%20district%20-%20in%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20retaliatory%20act.%20The%20victim%2C%20Bhaskar%20Jadhav%2C%20was%20blackened%20with%20paint%20by%20unidentified%20individuals.%20Days%20later%2C%20an%20ultra-luxury%20KSRTC%20bus%20was%20vandalised%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20with%20slogans%20like%20'Jai%20Maharashtra'%2C%20'Marathi'%2C%20and%20'Maharashtra%20Navnirman%20Sena'%20scribbled%20across%20its%20body%20in%20black%20paint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20tensions%20deepened%2C%20Maharashtra%20announced%20a%20halt%20to%20MSRTC%20bus%20services%20to%20Karnataka.%20The%20southern%20state%20also%20reduced%20its%20bus%20services%20to%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742611320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Ffvgdv51_karnataka-bandh_625x300_22_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnat