inID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Flsg-slammed-labelled-worst-franchise-ever-after-viral-social-media-storm-involving-david-miller-7973972%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20(LSG)%20have%20been%20heavily%20criticised%20for%20a%20social%20media%20post%20ahead%20of%20IPL%202025.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20Advice%20To%20Students%20In%20US%20As%20Trump's%20Deportation%20Policy%20Gains%20Pace%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20has%20advised%20its%20citizens%20studying%20in%20the%20US%20to%20comply%20with%20American%20laws%20after%20a%20researcher%20was%20arrested%20and%20another%20student%20had%20to%20self-deport%20to%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-is-badar-khan-suri-indian-researcher-in-us-facing-deportation-7965527%5C%22%3EBadar%20Khan%20Suri%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20postdoctoral%20fellow%20at%20Georgetown%20University%2C%20has%20been%20accused%20by%20US%20authorities%20of%20spreading%20%26quot%3BHamas%20propaganda%26quot%3B%20while%20Columbia%20University%C2%A0student%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findian-student-from-columbia-university-ranjani-srinivasan-self-deports-after-us-revokes-visa-over-palestine-protests-7926709%5C%22%3ERanjini%20Srinivasan%3C%2Fa%3E's%20visa%20was%20revoked%20for%20participating%20in%20pro-Palestine%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20Indians%20did%20not%20contact%20the%20Indian%20embassies%20in%20the%20US%20for%20assistance%2C%20said%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%2C%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20External%20Affairs%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Suri%20and%20Ms%20Srinivasan%20are%20among%20the%20latest%20academics%20targeted%20in%20the%20US%20crackdown%20on%20pro-Palestine%20campus%20protests.%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20has%20termed%20such%20individuals%20%26quot%3Bterrorist%20sympathizers%26quot%3B%2C%20has%20threatened%20to%20cut%20university%20funding%20and%20deport%20such%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20policy%20has%20shaken%20the%20academic%20world%20and%20students%20now%20fear%20losing%20their%20residency%20permit.%20US%20authorities%20insist%20on%20deporting%20Mr%20Suri%2C%20who%20has%20claimed%20that%20his%20wife's%20Palestinian%20roots%20led%20to%20his%20arrest%2C%20but%20a%20court%20recently%20blocked%20his%20removal%20from%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbadar-khan-suri-the-alleged-hamas-link-that-landed-indian-researcher-in-trouble-in-us-7974432%5C%22%3EThe%20Alleged%20Hamas%20Link%20That%20Landed%20Indian%20Researcher%20In%20Trouble%20In%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Srinivasan%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20take%20any%20chance.%20She%20left%20for%20Canada%20after%20her%20US%20visa%20was%20revoked%20for%20allegedly%20%26quot%3Badvocating%20for%20violence%20and%20terrorism%26quot%3B%20and%20her%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20activities%20supporting%20Hamas%2C%20a%20Palestinian%20group%20banned%20by%20the%20US%20and%20Israel.%20The%20doctoral%20student%20at%20Columbia%20University%20used%20the%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%20Home%20app%20to%20self-deport%20to%20Canada%20on%20March%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisa%20and%20immigration%20matters%20lie%20within%20a%20country's%20sovereign%20functions%2C%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20said%20on%20Friday%2C%20suggesting%20that%20the%20US%20has%20the%20right%20to%20decide%20such%20internal%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20that%20when%20we%20have%20foreign%20nationals%20coming%20to%20India%2C%20they%20abide%20by%20our%20laws%20and%20regulations.%20Similarly%2C%20we%20expect%20that%20when%20Indian%20nationals%20are%20abroad%2C%20they%20must%20also%20comply%20with%20local%20laws%20and%20regulations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20weekly%20briefing%2C%20he%20also%20assured%20the%20students%20that%20Indian%20consulates%20and%20embassies%20in%20the%20US%20would%20help%20them%20if%20they%20faced%20any%20difficulty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-columbia-student-ranjani-srinivasan-fled-from-us-amid-immigration-crackdown-7935689%5C%22%3EHow%20Ranjani%20Srinivasan%20Fled%20From%20US%20Amid%20Immigration%20Crackdown%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaiswal%20said%20that%20he%20had%20seen%20media%20reports%20on%20Mr%20Suri's%20detention%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bneither%20the%20US%20government%20nor%20this%20individual%20approached%20us%20or%20the%20embassy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20side%20was%20also%20not%20aware%20of%20Ms%20Srinivasan%20contacting%20any%20Indian%20consulate%20for%20help%2C%20said%20Mr%20Jaiswal.%20%26quot%3BWe%20only%20came%20to%20know%20of%20her%20departure%20from%20the%20US%20from%20media%20reports.%20We%20understand%20that%20she%20has%20gone%20to%20Canada%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20the%20MEA%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20a%20large%20and%20growing%20number%20of%20Indians%20are%20studying%20in%20American%20universities%20and%20the%20government%20wants%20to%20bolster%20the%20educational%20ties%20with%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20an%20Indian%20student%20is%20facing%20any%20problem%2C%20the%20consulate%20or%20the%20embassy%20is%20there%20to%20help%20them%20with%20their%20well-being%20(and)%20safety.%20We%20would%20continue%20if%20there%20is%20any%20Indian%20student%20who%20would%20like%20a%20helping%20hand.%20Our%20Consulate%20and%20our%20Government%2C%20the%20Embassy%20is%20there%20to%20help%20them%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742611020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-01%2Fja0qh5ng_us-college-us-university-generic-pixa