the%20world%20to%20marvel%20at%20advancements%20across%20the%20industry%20that%20were%20showcased%20during%20Nvidia's%20annual%20GTC%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Nvidia%20has%20hosted%20GTC%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0that's%20short%20for%20GPU%20Technology%20Conference%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0since%202009%2C%20the%20event%20has%20expanded%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20and%20a%20half%20to%20highlight%20not%20just%20advancements%20in%20semiconductors%2C%20accelerated%20computing%2C%20and%20artificial%20intelligence%20but%20also%20robotics%2C%20autonomous%20and%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20and%20future-looking%20technology%20like%20quantum%20computing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20have%20noticed%20that%20the%20feeling%20of%20GTC%20has%20really%20changed%2C%26quot%3B%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20said%20in%20a%20Thursday%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20he's%20right%2C%20the%20event%20%3Cem%3Ehas%20%3C%2Fem%3Echanged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20weren't%20able%20to%20attend%20GTC%20this%20year%2C%20here's%20what%20you%20missed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f3bec2c6-3fb8-4826-9a59-1a2392a4321a%5C%22%3EAI%20is%20big%20business%20now%2C%20and%20the%20stakes%20are%20higher%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20last%20year's%20GTC%20keynote%2C%20Huang%20mentioned%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Brevenue%26quot%3B%20once.%20This%20year%20it%20was%20mentioned%2010%20times.%20The%20message%20was%20that%20it's%20time%20for%20everyone%20in%20the%20AI%20ecosystem%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20Nvidia%20%E2%80%94%20to%20make%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20keynote%2C%20Huang%20emphasized%20Nvidia's%20evolution%20from%20a%20chip%20company%20to%20an%20AI%20infrastructure%20company%20that%20sells%20%26quot%3BAI%20factories.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20described%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-ai-factory-tokens-2025-3%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%2522I%2520call%2520them%2520AI%2520factories%2C%252C%2520into%2520chemicals%2520or%2520proteins.%2522%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20factories%3C%2Fa%3E%20produce%20intelligence%2C%20and%20the%20most%20productive%20factory%20should%20be%20the%20most%20successful.%20Huang%20said%20the%20quality%20of%20each%20company's%20AI%20factory%20will%20have%20a%20big%20impact%20on%20its%20overall%20revenue.%20And%20that%20applies%20to%20any%20industry%2C%20whether%20it's%20traditionally%20in%20%26quot%3Btech%26quot%3B%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20industry%20is%20here.%20Every%20country%20is%20here%2C%20and%20every%20company%20is%20here%20because%20we%20have%20become%20a%20foundational%20company%20by%20which%20other%20companies%20are%20built%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20told%20reporters%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2213344f7b-0f55-4890-abb5-4c911fc38084%5C%22%3ENvidia%20is%20at%20the%20center%20of%20the%20AI%20ecosystem%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Nvidia's%20technology%20enables%20most%20of%20the%20innovation%20in%20AI%20today%2C%20it%20also%20sets%20the%20bar%20for%20what's%20possible%20%E2%80%94%20how%20fantastically%20engineers%20can%20apply%20their%20imaginations.%20The%20next%20round%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gtc-keynote-live-jensen-huang-rubin-blackwell-ultra-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echip%20architecture%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Huang%20described%20in%20his%20keynote%20address%20drew%20a%20small%20gasp%20from%20the%20audience%20in%20the%20room%20due%20to%20the%20power%20and%20performance%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECloud%20companies%20and%20AI%20developers%20at%20the%20conference%20told%20BI%20the%20ecosystem%20is%20still%20wrapping%20its%20head%20around%20what%20massive%20advances%20in%20chip%20performance%20will%20mean%20for%20what%20developers%20can%20build%20and%20what%20other%20players%20in%20the%20infrastructure%20ecosystem%20need%20to%20prepare.%20That's%20why%2C%20Huang%20explained%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20several%20generations%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20everybody%20else%20can%20plan%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20Thursday%20press%20conference.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20good%20old%20days%2C%20you're%20building%20chips.%20Somebody%20buys%20a%20chip%2C%20they%20put%20it%20in%20the%20computer%2C%20they%20sell%20a%20computer.%20What%20we%20do%20now%20is%20we%20build%20AI%20infrastructure%20that%20are%20deployed%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20at%20a%20time%2C%20and%20so%20you%20better%20do%20a%20good%20job%20planning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2229970814-62a7-4f83-9fb5-eb6b552dc4b5%5C%22%3EThe%20cadence%20of%20AI%20innovation%20has%20picked%20up%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20an%20urgency%20in%20the%20halls%20of%20the%20San%20Jose%20Convention%20Center%2C%20likely%20due%20to%20packed%20schedules%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gtc-2025-ceo-jensen-huang-ai-landscape-san-jose-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong%20lines%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20the%20pace%20of%20AI%20model%20innovation%20has%20quickened%20too%2C%20and%20in%20side%20conversations%2C%20press%20conferences%2C%20and%20panels%20the%20refrain%20was%20that%20each%20new%20paradigm%20lasts%20about%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia's%20Senior%20Director%20of%20High-Performance%20Computing%20and%20AI%20Factory%20Solutions%20Dion%20Harris%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20stakeholders%20he%20spends%20time%20with%20in%20his%20day-to-day%20work%20is%20cutting-edge%20researchers.%20They%20are%20closer%20to%20what's%20coming%20next%20and%20can%20potentially%20drive%20the%20most%20value%2C%20for%20example%2C%20from%20the%20AI%20factory%20model%2C%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f1d3d082-7a8a-4338-b86a-b9227be7ee29%5C%22%3ERobots%20are%20coming%2C%20but%20they're%20not%20here%20yet%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20exhibition%20floor%20featured%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gtc-2025-ceo-jensen-huang-ai-landscape-san-jose-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evariety%20of%20robots%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20self-driving%20cars%20to%20underscore%20what%20Huang%20said%20in%20his%20keynote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20described%20robots%20as%20a%20substitute%20for%20human%20labor%20in%20short%20supply%2C%20the%20key%20that%20could%20make%20every%20car%20self-driving%20and%20an%20essential%20technology%20in%20taking%20physical%20action%20on%20much%20of%20the%20intelligence%20we%20can%20create%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPhysical%20AI%20and%20robotics%20are%20moving%20so%20fast%2C%20everybody%2C%20pay%20attention%20to%20this%20space.%20This%20could%20very%20well%20likely%20be%20the%20largest%20industry%20of%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said%20in%20his%20keynote%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20robotic%20future%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-nvidia-robots-huamanoid-self-driving-cars-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimportant%20to%20Nvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20leveraging%20AI%20to%20understand%20the%20physical%20universe%20and%20take%20action%20in%20three%20dimensions%20will%20require%20an%20immense%20amount%20of%20compute.%20And%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eif%20it%20remains%20the%20titan%20provider%20of%20computing%20power%20it%20is%20today%2C%20it%20is%20expected%20to%20raise%20Nvidia's%20profile%20even%20further%20as%20it%20becomes%20the%20foundation%20of%20a%20new%20industry.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBut%20many%20of%20the%20robots%20on%20display%20in%20the%20convenient%20center%20are%20nascent%20in%20their%20capabilities%20or%20still%20in%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20announced%20a%20new%20open-source%20reasoning%20model%20for%20robotics%20aimed%20at%20accelerating%20out%20of%20the%20development%20phases%20Tuesday.%20The%20new%20model%20could%20make%20robots%20able%20to%20adjust%20to%20different%20tasks%20and%20environments%20on%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20