%22title%22%3A%22Never%20Accepted%20Illegal%20Chinese%20Occupation%20Of%20Indian%20Territory%3A%20Centre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20aware%20of%20China%20establishing%20two%20new%20counties%2C%20parts%20of%20which%20fall%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20and%20has%20registered%20a%20%26quot%3Bsolemn%26quot%3B%20protest%20through%20diplomatic%20channels%2C%20the%20government%20told%20Parliament%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20never%20accepted%20the%20illegal%20Chinese%20occupation%20of%20Indian%20Territory%20in%20this%20area.%20Creation%20of%20new%20counties%20will%20neither%20have%20a%20bearing%20on%20India's%20long-standing%20and%20consistent%20position%20regarding%20India's%20sovereignty%20over%20the%20area%2C%20nor%20lend%20legitimacy%20to%20China's%20illegal%20and%20forcible%20occupation%20of%20the%20same%2C%26quot%3B%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20External%20Affairs%20Kirti%20Vardhan%20Singh%20said%20this%20in%20a%20written%20response%20to%20a%20query%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20registered%20its%20%26quot%3Bsolemn%20protest%20over%20these%20developments%20through%20diplomatic%20channels%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20was%20asked%20whether%20the%20government%20is%20aware%20of%20%26quot%3BChina's%20establishment%20of%20two%20new%20counties%20in%20the%20Hotan%20prefecture%2C%20incorporating%20Indian%20territory%20in%20Ladakh%26quot%3B%2C%20if%20so%2C%20the%20strategic%20and%20diplomatic%20measures%20undertaken%20by%20the%20government%20to%20address%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20query%20also%20sought%20details%20of%20protests%20lodged%20by%20India%20against%20the%20%26quot%3Bcreation%20of%20these%20counties%26quot%3B%20along%20with%20the%20responses%20received%20from%20the%20Chinese%20government%2C%20if%20any.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20asked%20whether%20the%20government%20has%20formulated%20any%20long-term%20strategies%20to%20%26quot%3Bcounter%20China's%20increasing%20administrative%20and%20infrastructural%20developments%20in%20the%20Aksai%20Chin%20region%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGovernment%20of%20India%20is%20aware%20of%20the%20announcement%20by%20the%20Chinese%20side%20pertaining%20to%20the%20establishment%20of%20so-called%20two%20new%20counties%20in%20Hotan%20prefecture%20of%20China.%20Parts%20of%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20these%20so-called%20counties%20fall%20in%20India's%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Ladakh%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20is%20also%20aware%20that%20China%20is%20%26quot%3Bdeveloping%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20border%20regions%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGovernment%20gives%20careful%20and%20special%20attention%20to%20improvement%20of%20infrastructure%20for%20the%20development%20of%20border%20areas%2C%20in%20order%20to%20facilitate%20the%20economic%20development%20of%20these%20areas%2C%20as%20also%20to%20meet%20India's%20strategic%20and%20security%20requirements%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MoS%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20budget%20allocation%20for%20border%20infrastructure%20have%20increased%20in%20the%20last%20decade%20(2014-2024).%20The%20Border%20Roads%20Organisation%20(BRO)%20alone%20has%20incurred%20three%20times%20the%20expenditure%20level%20compared%20to%20the%20decade%20before%2C%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20length%20of%20the%20road%20networks%2C%20bridges%20and%20number%20of%20tunnels%20have%20all%20seen%20a%20substantial%20increase%20over%20the%20earlier%20period.%20This%20has%20helped%20provide%20connectivity%20to%20the%20local%20population%20and%20better%20logistical%20support%20for%20our%20armed%20forces%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20continues%20to%20keep%20a%20constant%20watch%20on%20all%20developments%20having%20a%20bearing%20on%20India's%20security%20and%20takes%20all%20the%20necessary%20measures%20to%20safeguard%20its%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity%2C%20the%20minister%20underlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742606520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-04%2Findia-china-flags_650x400_61523324939.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnever-accepted-illegal-chinese-occupation-of-indian-territory-centre-7981007%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20is%20aware%20of%20China%20establishing%20two%20new%20counties%2C%20parts%20of%20which%20fall%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20and%20has%20registered%20a%20%26quot%3Bsolemn%26quot%3B%20protest%20through%20diplomatic%20channels%2C%20the%20government%20told%20Parliament%20on%20Friday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnever-accepted-illegal-chinese-occupation-of-indian-territory-centre-7981007%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Karnataka%20Doubles%20Salaries%20For%20Ministers%2C%20MLAs%20Amid%20Fund%20Shortage%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20Assembly%20on%20Friday%20passed%20the%20'Karnataka%20Legislature%20Salaries%2C%20Pensions%20and%20Allowances%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202025%2C%20which%20proposes%20significant%20salary%20hikes%20and%20allowances%20for%20MLAs%2C%20MLCs%2C%20ministers%20and%20Assembly%20staffers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20which%20has%20come%20amid%20the%20government%20complaining%20of%20shortage%20of%20funds%20has%20invoked%20criticism%20and%20also%20raised%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20Assembly%20amid%20the%20furore%20linked%20to%20the%20honey%20trap%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20Bill%20proposes%20100%20per%20cent%20hike%20of%20Rs%201.50%20lakh%20from%20Rs%2075%2C000%20in%20the%20salary%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20108%20per%20cent%20hike%20of%20Rs%201.25%20lakh%20from%20Rs%2060%2C000%20for%20ministers.%20The%20legislators%20will%20have%20100%20per%20cent%20hike%20of%20Rs%2080%2C000%20from%20Rs%2040%2C000.%20The%20rental%20allowance%20of%20ministers%20has%20also%20been%20doubled%20from%20Rs%201.20%20lakh%20to%20Rs%202.50%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Speaker%20of%20the%20Legislative%20Assembly%20and%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Legislative%20Council's%20monthly%20salary%20of%20Rs%2075%2C000%20will%20be%20increased%20to%20Rs%201.25%20lakh.%20Their%20allowances%20have%20been%20increased%20from%20Rs%204%20lakh%20to%20Rs%205%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernor%20Thaawarchand%20Gehlot%20approved%20the%20proposed%20Bill%20on%20Thursday.%20The%20government%20not%20delaying%20it%20any%20further%20presented%20it%20in%20the%20legislature%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20last%20day%20of%20the%20budget%20session.%20The%20government%20is%20expected%20to%20incur%20an%20additional%20burden%20of%20Rs%2062%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20salaries%20and%20allowance%20of%20legislators%20were%20revised%20in%202022.%20The%20government%20headed%20by%20the%20BJP%20had%20decided%20to%20revise%20the%20salaries%20and%20perks%20of%20legislators%20once%20in%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legislators%20had%20demanded%20a%20hike%20in%20the%20Business%20Advisory%20Committee%20(BAC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pension%20of%20legislators%20will%20go%20up%20from%20Rs%2050%2C000%20to%20Rs%2075%2C000.%20The%20annual%20travelling%20allowance%20to%20travel%20in%20flights%20and%20railway%20services%20has%20been%20increased%20to%20Rs%203.50%20lakh%20from%20Rs%202.50%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742606460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.nd