a%20different%20take%20on%20the%20traditional%20strapless%20bra%2C%20as%20it%20had%20extra%20fabric%20to%20create%20a%20corset-like%20fit.%20On%20the%20underwire%20bra%20itself%2C%20I%20felt%20it%20did%20pretty%20well%20in%20terms%20of%20keeping%20my%20bust%20supported%2C%20although%20it%20didn't%20have%20much%20padding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20its%20cups%20are%20thin%2C%20the%20firm%20construction%20meant%20my%20bust%20barely%20moved%20during%20the%20jumping%20jack%20test.%20That's%20even%20without%20a%20no-slip%20lining%20on%20the%20interior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20wings%2C%20despite%20being%20thin%2C%20were%20large%20and%20snug%20enough%20to%20support%20my%20bust.%20The%20four%20row%20hook-and-eye%20closure%20also%20had%20a%20barely-there%20feel%20and%20allowed%20for%20some%20give%20on%20the%20lowest%20level.%20While%20I%20really%20did%20like%20this%20bra%2C%20%2482%20is%20pretty%20expensive%20(unless%20you%20plan%20to%20wear%20it%20often).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETorrid%20Bombshell%20Everyday%20Strapless%20Push-Up%20Bra%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Black%20strapless%20bra.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67dc6a8cb8b41a9673fb44fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECasey%20Clark%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20wear%20push-up%20bras%20often%20because%20I%20already%20have%20a%20pretty%20big%20chest%2C%20but%20some%20necklines%20look%20better%20with%20a%20bit%20of%20lifted%20cleavage.%20That's%20exactly%20what%20this%20bra%20from%20Torrid%20did%20for%20me.%20For%20only%20%2429%2C%20it's%20a%20good%20value%20on%20a%20bra.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20heavily%20padded%20cups%2C%20with%20most%20of%20the%20padding%20being%20towards%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20cup%20to%20give%20the%20desired%20push-up%20effect.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20cup%20is%20pretty%20padded%2C%20too.%20I%20liked%20the%20no-slip%20sil