de%20the%20four%20rows%20of%20hook-and-eye%20closures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20qualm%20I%20had%20with%20this%20bra%20was%20that%20the%20cups%20were%20a%20bit%20flimsy.%20They%20didn't%20stick%20to%20my%20skin%20at%20the%20top%20of%20my%20chest%20as%20much%20as%20I%20would%20have%20liked%20it%20to%2C%20so%20there%20was%20some%20slight%20gapping.%20My%20bust%20moved%20slightly%20more%20in%20this%20bra%20during%20testing%2C%20so%20I'd%20hesitate%20to%20wear%20it%20with%20a%20low-cut%20top.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EStill%2C%20this%20didn't%20impede%20the%20bra's%20ability%20to%20stay%20up%2C%20and%20underneath%20a%20high-neck%20blouse%20it%20would%20be%20more%20than%20fine.%20It%20costs%20%2462%2C%20but%20because%20it%20comes%20with%20straps%20and%20offers%20ample%20support%2C%20you'll%20be%20able%20to%20lower%20its%20cost-per-wear%20in%20no%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20I%20tested%20the%20best%20strapless%20bras%20for%20large%20busts%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20the%20best%20strapless%20bras%20for%20large%20busts%2C%20I%20wore%20each%20bra%20for%20two%20days%20at%20a%20time%20while%20going%20about%20my%20usual%20routine%2C%20like%20going%20on%20brisk%20walks%2C%20doing%20household%20chores%2C%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20other%20random%20errands.%20I%20paid%20attention%20to%20how%20comfortable%20they%20were%20throughout%20the%20day%20and%20if%20they%20were%20a%20pain%20to%20take%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20I%20did%2015%20jumping%20jacks%20in%20each%20strapless%20bra%20to%20simulate%20light%20physical%20activity%20and%20chose%20the%20bras%20that%20stayed%20put%20around%20my%20ribcage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20the%20best%20strapless%20bras%20for%20large%20busts%3Cp%3EKimmay%20Caldwell%20is%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhurraykimmay.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpert%20in%20bra-fitting%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewho%20has%20helped%20literally%20thousands%20of%20people%2C%20ranging%20from%20cups%20sizes%20AA%20to%20N%2C%20with%20finding%20the%20perfect%20bra.%20We%20discussed%20which%20factors%20are%20ideal%20in%20a%20strapless%20bra%20for%20D%20cups%20and%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESupportive%20underwire.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESince%20a%20strapless%20bra%20can't%20rely%20on%20straps%20to%20hold%20everything%20in%20place%2C%20it%20needs%20features%20to%20help%20lift%20your%20bust%20and%20keep%20its%20band%20secure.%20%26quot%3BFor%20some%2C%20molded%20or%20contour%20cups%20and%20an%20underwire%20will%20create%20a%20sturdy%20frame%20in%20the%20front%20that%20will%20retain%20its%20shape%2C%26quot%3B%20Caldwell%20says.%20You%20should%20also%20look%20for%20bras%20with%20silicone%20strips%20that%20prevent%20the%20bra's%20liner%20from%20slipping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirm%20fabrics.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYou'll%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20you%20also%20have%20a%20snug%2C%20slightly%20stiff%20band%20to%20give%20you%20the%20extra%20support%20needed%20when%20wearing%20a%20strapless%20bra.%20%26quot%3BSomething%20too%20thin%20or%20stretchy%20might%20not%20stay%20put%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20adds.%20%26quot%3BThat%20might%20mean%20multiple%20rows%20and%20columns%20of%20hooks%20and%20eyes%20so%20you%20can%20adjust%20the%20band%20as%20needed%20for%20a%20secure%20fit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20sturdy%20band.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYour%20bra%20should%20feel%20lightly%20compressive%20(but%20not%20constricting)%20in%20order%20to%20be%20comfortable%20for%20long-term%20wear.%20%26quot%3BThe%20right%20strapless%20bra%20will%20hug%20your%20body%20without%20digging%20in%20or%20slipping%20down%2C%20so%20you%20can%20go%20about%20your%20day%20%E2%80%94%20or%20night%E2%80%94%20without%20constantly%20readjusting%2C%26quot%3B%20Caldwell%20tells%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExtended%20hook-and-eye%20closure.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Most%20bras%20have%20three%20rows%20of%20hook-and-eye%20closures%2C%20which%20works%20for%20people%20with%20smaller%20busts.%20But%20if%20you're%20large-chested%2C%20a