actor%20negligence%20or%20defective%20material.%20It%20could%20also%20be%20that%20this%20incident%20occurred%20when%20critical%20components%20were%20due%20to%20be%20upgraded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESomething%20like%20this%20happening%20is%20incredibly%20rare.%20We're%20all%20focused%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20single-point%20failure%20has%20had%20such%20a%20significant%20economic%20impact%20for%20one%20day.%20It%20shows%20how%20vulnerable%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcyber-attacks-against-our-critical-infrastructure-are-likely-to-increase-2016-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecritical%20infrastructure%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20aren't%20a%20lot%20of%20specialists%20who%20really%20understand%20the%20energy%20and%20infrastructure%20space%2C%20but%20I've%20been%20in%20this%20business%20for%20years.%20It%20gives%20me%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20unique%20vantage%20point.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20company%2C%20Nardac%2C%20works%20with%20energy%20and%20infrastructure%20companies%20on%20their%20investments.%20We%20act%20as%20a%20broker%20%E2%80%94%20helping%20our%20clients%20get%20appropriate%20insurance%20coverage%20when%20they%20invest%20in%20things%20like%20critical%20infrastructure%20projects.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETypically%2C%20larger%20losses%20in%20the%20energy%20infrastructure%20market%20are%20driven%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworst-natural-disasters-2018-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enatural%20catastrophes%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Elike%20hurricanes%20or%20floods.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20doesn't%20seem%20like%20any%20natural%20issues%20were%20involved%20here.%20From%20what%20I%20understand%2C%20there%20wasn't%20lightning%20in%20the%20area%20that%20could%20have%20caused%20the%20transformers%20to%20c