0much%20closure%2C%20patience%20and%20understanding%20in%20knowing%20that%20you%20will%20not%20have%20to%20be%20discovered%20lifeless%20by%20somebody%20else%2C%20not%20a%20train%20conductor%2C%20not%20your%20sibling%2C%20not%20your%20friends%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Joseph%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20will%20have%20a%20non-violent%20end%20to%20your%20life%20with%20medical%20assistance%2C%20with%20support%2C%20with%20closure%20for%20those%20who%20love%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20Mr%20Joesph%20shared%20his%20story%20publicly%2C%20he%20has%20received%20mixed%20reactions.%20While%20some%20expressed%20that%20they%20respected%20his%20decision%2C%20others%20urged%20him%20to%20change%20his%20mind.%20He%20also%20received%20more%20than%20100%20messages%20from%20strangers%20inviting%20him%20to%20have%20dinner%20with%20them%2C%20which%20quickly%20inspired%20him%20to%20launch%20his%20worldwide%20dinner%20tour%20called%20'The%20Last%20Supper%20Project'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EPeople%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20so%20far%2C%20Mr%20Joseph%20has%20travelled%20to%20Paris%2C%20Milan%2C%20Brussels%2C%20and%20Berlin%20for%2057%20dinners%2C%20which%20he's%20documented%20on%20social%20media.%20He%20has%20over%20120%20more%20dinners%20planned%20through%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%2C%20'As%20I%20work%20with%20this%20non-violent%20transition%20in%20my%20life%2C%20why%20don't%20I%20connect%20with%20people%20to%20break%20bread%3F'%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Joesph%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%26quot%3BI%20find%20that%20I%20quite%20literally%20was%20made%20to%20interact%20with%20people%20this%20way%2C%20it's%20such%20a%20beautiful%2C%20organic%20part%20of%20my%20life.%20It%20doesn't%20feel%20difficult%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BI%20enjoy%20decentering%20myself%20from%20my%20life%20and%20being%20a%20part%20of%20other%20people's%20during%20dinner.%20I%20do%20find%20great%20fulfilment%20in%20connecting%20with%20people%20this%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fgen-z-managers-reason-for-rejecting-paid-time-off-requests-praised-online-7976535%5C%22%3EGen%20Z%20Manager's%20Reason%20For%20Rejecting%20Paid%20Time-Off%20Requests%20Praised%20Online%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2028-year-old%20still%20regularly%20shares%20videos%20of%20how%20much%20he%20still%20struggles%20with%20his%20bipolar%20disorder.%20While%20he%20appreciates%20the%20sense%20of%20community%20from%20the%20dinners%2C%20he%20said%20he%20feels%20neither%20better%20nor%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20still%20do%20wake%20up%20with%20breathing%2C%20really%20profound%20pain%20attached%20to%20my%20bipolar%20disorder.%20There's%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20ambivalence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20outlet.%20%26quot%3BI%20hope%20that%20(people%20with%20chronic%20mental%20illness)%20feel%20seen%20through%20my%20existence%20and%20my%20decision%20to%20live%20as%20authentically%20as%20possible.%20If%20I%20end%20up%20doing%20this%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20upset%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Mental%20Health%2C%20bipolar%20disorder%20is%20a%20manic-depressive%20illness%20of%20the%20brain%20that%20causes%20extreme%20changes%20in%20mood%20and%20energy%20levels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742570700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F7m7641e8_joseph-awuahdarko_625x300_21_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-man-28-opts-for-euthanasia-rather-than-living-with-mental-illness-documents-his-last-supper-with-strangers-7978536%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2028-year-old%20British-Ghanaian%20artist%20has%20opted%20to%20end%20his%20life%20with%20euthanasia%20rather%20than%20continue%20living%20with%20a%20